      "rationale": "Large-deformation continuum FEA with frictional contact (mu=0.3, titanium-UHMWPE interface) selected as appropriate model form for static compression-bending. Inter-laboratory spread across three independent models used to estimate model form uncertainty contribution. All three models predict QoIs within the acceptance band. Gradation 3 achieved."
