      "rationale": "Testing performed per ASTM F1717 at a single static compression-bending load condition (ambient, dry). Only one test configuration evaluated; multi-condition or multi-load-level testing not conducted. This limits the achieved level to Gradation 2 against a Gradation 3 requirement. This gap is acknowledged and accepted given that the COU is restricted to the single validated configuration."
