      "rationale": "One-to-one correspondence established between FEA model inputs and physical test measurements. Fixture geometry in FEA matched to measured ASTM F1717 fixture dimensions. Material properties from same lot as tested specimens. Traceability matrix linking each FEA input to its physical measurement source documented in the simulation report. Gradation 3 achieved."
