      "rationale": "For all three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm), E/uval < 1.96 and percent difference in mean < 10% confirmed across all three modeling teams. Stiffness: E/uval = 0.87, 4.2% difference. Yield force: E/uval = 1.12, 6.1% difference. Force at 40 mm: E/uval = 0.94, 3.8% difference. Acceptance criteria met. Gradation 3 achieved."
